{"tid":1718594,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［發夢攻略研究］你地唔好亂咁用雞尾酒la","createTime":"2019-11-14T01:32:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T16:31:32.000Z","uid":41366,"like":38,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"97589a63f69f8c3602d319af7861b2eedc9f9240","tid":1718594,"uid":41366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T01:32:17.000Z","msg":"有位中學教師同我講，睇下work唔work<br />\n1. 首先向目標投擲大量無火既雞尾酒<br />\n2 之後一定會成地酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，但對方因覺得你哋無料到，自然輕敵啦<br />\n3. 到對方一衝上來，將一支堅野掉出去，衝上黎既敵人，因地上已經有很多......， 隨即身陷險境<br />\n<br />\n又阻對方前進, 又有佢估你唔到既效果<br />\n只要最後幾個人可以擲出堅野<br />\n到時大家就可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1e41695ad98846ad8bdf133a06ea66ca79903a5","tid":1718594,"uid":313764,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T01:36:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MLRtWzR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMLRtWzR.jpg&h=3337de01&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n幻想下入邊唔係水而係魔法液，我就真係唔敢衝啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27aa224b3dc3f1de2567ebc335b4ebf9710d9b2f","tid":1718594,"uid":41366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T01:38:15.000Z","msg":"有冇機會可以試吓"},{"pid":"b1dd24b3adcf99e6e5857335f6bdc1ad790a5619","tid":1718594,"uid":13638,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d1e41695ad98846ad8bdf133a06ea66ca79903a5","tid":1718594,"uid":313764,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T01:36:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MLRtWzR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMLRtWzR.jpg&h=3337de01&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n幻想下入邊唔係水而